# Testing Strategy (测试策略)

Scope: all DTS projects

## Test Pyramid

```
        /  E2E  \           ← Playwright (3 webapps) + Business E2E (5 critical paths)
       / Integration \      ← API tests per service, cross-service chain tests
      /    Unit Tests   \   ← Per-service, fast, isolated
     /   AI Evaluation    \ ← Evaluation suites, accuracy tracking, regression gates
```

## Unit Tests

- Every service must have unit tests covering core business logic.
- Python: pytest + pytest-asyncio. Minimum 80% coverage on core/ directory.
- Java: JUnit 5 + Mockito. Minimum 80% coverage on service/repository layers.
- Go: standard testing + testify. Minimum 80% coverage on internal/ packages.
- Frontend: Vitest + Testing Library. Test user interactions, not implementation details.
- Unit tests must NOT depend on external services (DB, Kafka, etc.). Use mocks/fakes.

## Integration Tests

- Test service API contracts (gRPC + REST).
- Python: pytest + grpcio-testing or httpx.
- Java: Spring Boot Test + Testcontainers (PG, Kafka, Redis).
- Go: integration test with test fixtures.
- Each service must have integration tests that cover: happy path, auth failure, permission denied, invalid input.

## E2E Tests

- Playwright for frontend E2E across all 3 webapps.
- 5 critical business paths (from product v2.4.1):
  1. Data ingestion → metadata sync → data visibility
  2. AI modeling recommendation → HITL approval → execution → result verification
  3. NL query → chart generation → dashboard → screen publish
  4. Auth login → RBAC permission → AI conversation → approval flow
  5. Quality rule → alert → fix action → AI review

## AI Evaluation

- Managed by dts-ai-eval service.
- Every AI capability (NL2SQL, intent routing, ontology mapping) must have an evaluation suite.
- Minimum 50 test cases per capability.
- Metrics tracked: accuracy, latency P95, token cost, hallucination rate.
- Bad Case flywheel: failed cases automatically collected → reviewed → added to test suite.
- Regression gate: new deployment must not decrease accuracy below baseline.

## AppPack Testing

- Every Pack must include evaluation dataset (minimum 50 cases) for its Skills.
- Pack integration test: install → capabilities registered → skill callable → uninstall → clean.
- Pack frontend modules must have basic smoke tests.
